article.headline: Miller scores 16, Temple downs Rice 65-43

images.name: Temple Owls vs. Rice Owls: Game Highlights
images.caption: Temple Owls vs. Rice Owls: Game Highlights

article.story: HOUSTON -- — Hysier Miller scored 16 points as Temple beat Rice 65-43 on Wednesday night. Miller also added four steals for the Owls (11-17, 4-11 American Athletic Conference). Sam Hofman, Steve Settle III and Matteo Picarelli each scored eight points. Hofman and Settle combined for 16 rebounds. The Owls (11-17, 5-10) were led in scoring by Max Fiedler, who finished with 12 points and nine rebounds. Mekhi Mason added nine points and three steals for Rice. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
